            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>eo</ex></expan> Atti <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Cantin</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><abbr>Capell</abbr> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 5 befindet sich auf der crepido. Vielleicht Capell(a) oder Capell(ianus). Reste von weißer Farbe in den Buchstaben.</p>
            </div>
